{"tid":2160851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳成全球首個實現5G獨立組網全覆蓋城市","createTime":"2020-08-17T08:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T09:51:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"88adcdb2cd16761f5b316691cd292c5b9da66d5f","tid":2160851,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:34:53.000Z","msg":"深圳成全球首個實現5G獨立組網全覆蓋城市<br />\n2小時前  Share to Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=402039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402039&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d66b1ea0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402039&h=fef42586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=402039</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】深圳宣布成為中國首個，亦是全球首個5G獨立組網全覆蓋的城市，會在醫療、教育、交通、工業、互聯網等多方面投入服務。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市召開5G智慧之城發布會，市長陳如桂宣布深圳率先進入5G時代，成為中國首個，亦是全球第一個實現5G獨立組網全覆蓋的城市。<br />\n<br />\n截至上周五，深圳已建成46480個5G基站，基站密度國內第一。據當局披露，5G基站7月底時，已建設到45000個，比原定目標快了一個月。<br />\n<br />\n目前深圳的5G產業規模、5G基站和終端出貨量都屬全球第一。華為、中興等公司是當地的5G產業鏈重點企業，在網絡建設、場景應用和終端領域方面居領導地位。<br />\n<br />\n場景應用方面，深圳已在交通、警務、醫療、教育、旅遊等十個方面，及聯網無人機和工業互聯網等十個行業，確定「雙十」5G應用示範項目，總投資超過十六億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n多個重要區域已實現移動5G網絡覆蓋，包括深圳寶安國際機場、市民中心等交通樞紐及核心商圈。<br />\n<br />\n當局亦計劃首批88個新基建項目，投資超過4000億元人民幣，改善訊息基礎設施，進而帶動新技術、新消費。<br />\n<br />\n當局指下一步是要致力改良5G技術，在基礎材料與核心零件實現突破，實施「補鏈、穩鏈、強鏈」工程，形成5G產業全鏈發展，深化工業互聯網、智慧港口等行業融合應用，將深圳打造成5G全球標桿城市。"},{"pid":"595aa8e074bad471b489bf266878cde803fb887a","tid":2160851,"uid":343754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"深圳好似都唔係全部地方都收到4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e992c8e13c35e4d7234fffc7064ed11c717c520e","tid":2160851,"uid":16981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"但係速度比3G還要慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e43aeb7d492310d5468e6335a63f11debadbdb","tid":2160851,"uid":289214,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"上唔上到facebook？收唔收到whatapps？load pornhub 會唔會快D？"},{"pid":"2a6a8ff02c95ca4cea733f6f70f82fa5f066f2dd","tid":2160851,"uid":11454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:49:42.000Z","msg":"裝機站<br />\n無視所有安全限制, 所有私隱條例, 所有對人體有害既電子功率限制<br />\n其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0588153d617b252e18730ae0499a43cd98efd4","tid":2160851,"uid":273218,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"595aa8e074bad471b489bf266878cde803fb887a","tid":2160851,"uid":343754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"深圳好似都唔係全部地方都收到4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"基本上係人都知地鐵同公交<br />\n連王者榮耀都打唔到<br />\n係中移4G plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac70f838e676f32d21f5cb35d2134c44111767f0","tid":2160851,"uid":63734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:52:20.000Z","msg":"5G內聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4c510694ca747b31b01d6056a6c0082fbf7c2a","tid":2160851,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"595aa8e074bad471b489bf266878cde803fb887a","tid":2160851,"uid":343754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:42:13.000Z","msg":"深圳好似都唔係全部地方都收到4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:52:28.000Z","msg":"羅湖金光華廣場長期lag 網<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8759d4bf369614df3b03e20484ff346a15f2c5b","tid":2160851,"uid":59929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T08:52:47.000Z","msg":"中